OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FKemi Badenoch clashes with 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FMPs over menopause law     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Equalities Minister Kemi Badenoch has  
OL,6, rejected calls to make it illegal to   
OL,7, discriminate against people going      
OL,8, through the menopause.                 
OL,10,FA committee of MPs is demanding that   
OL,11,Fmenopause be made a "protected         
OL,12,Fcharacteristic" under equalities law.  
OL,14,FMs Badenoch said people asked for "many
OL,15,Fthings" to be protected in law such as 
OL,16,F"carers, single people, having ginger  
OL,17,Fhair, being short".                    
OL,19,FBut the government would not be        
OL,20,Fchanging the legislation, she told MPs.
